ZH: 我的药方已经过期了，我需要去看医生开新的。
EN: My prescription has expired, I need to see a doctor for a new one.

ZH: 医生给我开了一份药方，需要每天服用三次。
EN: The doctor gave me a prescription that needs to be taken three times a day.

ZH: 请带上你的药方去药店购买所需药物。
EN: Please bring your prescription to the pharmacy to purchase the required medication.

ZH: 这种药是需凭药方购买的。
EN: This medication can only be purchased with a prescription.

ZH: 她的药方上写着要避免食用海鲜。
EN: It is written on her prescription to avoid consuming seafood.

ZH: 这个药方上的药需要到药房领取。
EN: The medication on this prescription needs to be collected from the pharmacy.

ZH: 请仔细阅读药方上的服用说明。
EN: Please read the dosage instructions on the prescription carefully.

ZH: 她跟医生沟通了病情，然后医生给她开了一份药方。
EN: She discussed her condition with the doctor, and the doctor gave her a prescription.

ZH: 我的喉咙疼，希望医生能开一份药方给我。
EN: My throat hurts, I hope the doctor can give me a prescription.

ZH: 这家药店接受电子药方吗？
EN: Does this pharmacy accept electronic prescriptions?

ZH: 医生开的这个药方有效吗？
EN: Is this prescription from the doctor effective?

ZH: 药方上写着要在饭后服用。
EN: It is written on the prescription to take the medication after meals.

ZH: 我从医生那里拿到了我的新药方。
EN: I got my new prescription from the doctor.

ZH: 药方上的药物非常昂贵。
EN: The medication on the prescription is very expensive.

ZH: 药方上写着每天服用两片。
EN: It is written on the prescription to take two tablets per day.

ZH: 我要去药房领取我的药方上的药物。
EN: I need to go to the pharmacy to collect the medication on my prescription.

ZH: 我的药方上的药已经用完了，我需要去开新的。
EN: I have run out of the medication on my prescription, I need to get a new one.

ZH: 请将药方备份保存在安全的地方。
EN: Please keep a backup of your prescription in a safe place.

ZH: 药房工作人员会核对药方上的药物名称与数量。
EN: Pharmacy staff will verify the medication name and quantity on the prescription.

ZH: 药方上的药服用后会有副作用吗？
EN: Are there any side effects after taking the medication on the prescription?
